name: Enny Rodriguez Developer
body:
### Welcome to my Page.

My name is Enny Rodríguez. I am from Caracas, Venezuela. I am graduated in  Informatics engineering. 


At the moment I am working as a software engineer consultant at a multinational company developing a datawarehouse solution to a international Bank. 

### My Skills
I have been interested in algorithms and data structures and its implementations especially in many languages since university. Later on I got acquainted with machine learning techniques, artificial intelligence in python(Now using TensorFlow for personal project), numerical methods and recipes such as solving differential equations, linear algebra, interpolation and extrapolation with C. These things may prove to be very very important in several fields: software engineering, videogames development, research and development or investment banking. I have a special addiction to big data, Bussiness Intelligence and quantitative models.


### Passion

I have willingness to embrace the concept of iterative development as the means for building excellent products, also Readiness to give all the effort necessary to do an excellent job - even if it means putting in extra time to research the problem i could be facing.

Excellent communication skills

### Support or Contact
Having trouble with Pages?, systems?, BI or Big Data Solutions? Check out our [Organization](https://www.femto.com.ve) or [contact support](https://ennydev.com.ve) and we’ll help you sort it out also ask for price quotation for your idea for a new app, web or system i can make that idea a real product for you!.
